\label{th22}
The number of smooth cyclic words of length $n$ over the alphabet $[k]$ is given by
$$\textit{scw}_{n,k}=\sum\limits_{j=1}^k\left[1+2\cos\Bigl(\frac{j\pi}{k+1}\Bigr)\right]^n.$$

\label{th3}
Let $n\geq1$. The number $\textit{sn}_{n,k}$ of smooth necklaces of length $n$ over an alphabet of $k$ letters is given by
$$
