Having defined $ \val_{(r,s)}\langle \textbf{T},\textbf{a}\rangle $ for every rooted tree $\langle \textbf{T},\textbf{a}\rangle, $ we define $ \val_{(r+1,s)}\langle \textbf{T},\textbf{a}\rangle\in\valc(r+1,s) $ as follows. For every $ \sigma\in\valc(r,s), $ let  
