where $ \langle \textbf{T},b\rangle $ is the subtree of $ \textbf{T} $ consisting of $ b $ as a root and all its children. Set
\[ \val_{(r+1,s)}\langle \textbf{T},\textbf{a}\rangle(\sigma):= 
